OL,3,CArmed officer fires weapon following
OL,4,Creports of someone with a knife
OL,6,FDyfed-Powys Police are carrying out
OL,7,Finquiries after a firearm officer
OL,8,Ffired a single shot from their weapon
OL,9,Fon the evening of the 28th of March at
OL,10,Fan address in Milford Haven.
OL,12,FThe police force said they received a
OL,13,Freport at 5.45pm of an individual who
OL,14,Fwas said to be in possession of a
OL,15,Fknife. Officers, including a firearms
OL,16,Funit, were dispatched to the property.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
