PN,46202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774868573
OL,3,CArmed officer fires weapon following
OL,4,Creports of someone with a knife
OL,6,FWhilst at the scene, the police
OL,7,Fdischarged a single shot from their
OL,8,Ffirearm at 6.32pm. The force said the
OL,9,Ffirearm was not directed towards an
OL,10,Findividual, and no injuries were
OL,11,Freported.
OL,13,FDyfed-Powys Police have voluntarily
OL,14,Freferred themselves to the Independent
OL,15,FOffice for Police Conduct.
OL,17,FA police presence has remained at the
OL,18,Fscene on the 29th of March.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
