OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774868573
OL,3,CArmed officer fires weapon following
OL,4,Creports of someone with a knife
OL,6,FDeputy Chief Constable Gary Phillips
OL,7,Fsaid: 'We have initiated a prompt
OL,8,Finvestigation into the circumstances
OL,9,Fthat led to the firearms being
OL,10,Fdischarged, and have referred the
OL,11,Fincident to the Independent Office for
OL,12,FPolice Conduct. We will work with them
OL,13,Fas we continue to establish the
OL,14,Fcircumstances leading up to the
OL,15,Fdischarge.'
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/4
