PN,46204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774868573
OL,3,CArmed officer fires weapon following
OL,4,Creports of someone with a knife
OL,6,FA spokesman for the Independent Office
OL,7,Ffor Police Conduct said: "We were
OL,8,Fnotified by Dyfed-Powys Police about
OL,9,Fthis incident on Saturday and advised
OL,10,Fthat a police firearm was discharged
OL,11,Fbut no injuries were reported.
OL,13,F"We understand a voluntary conduct
OL,14,Freferral is being made by the force,
OL,15,Fwhich we will assess before deciding
OL,16,Fwhether any further action is required
OL,17,Fby us."
